data.description: A rare opportunity to acquire property in the highly demanded Edgewater, FL 32141 area.  This 4 bedroom,  3 bath  1,875 sqft home was built in 1978. Nestled in an enjoyable, quiet neighborhood, minutes from I-95, local attractions, public transportation, and public park. $50,000 in renovations completed, but still need some TLC. Don't miss this great opportunity!
